<p>ABSTRACT</p>
<p>The Smart Home Services Management System is an online platform that allows users to seamlessly book multiple home maintenance services such as plumbing, electrical work, cleaning, and painting. The platform maintains a powerful Admin dashboard that allows syncing of data across the web and mobile interfaces automatically. You can effortlessly request a service online by picking your preferred service category. Once tailored features like time slots and addresses are finalized, the request is dispatched to nearby Service Providers. </p>
<p>Admins monitor everything in the management system. Admins can upload and update the service categories, calculate platform commissions, and verify the KYC (Know Your Customer) documentation of service providers to ensure safety. The resident (user) can view service details, use GPS location to provide exact coordinates, and fill out job requirements. The application features a real-time Chat and Notification system utilizing WebSockets.</p>
<p>This Smart Home Services Management System is developed using the MERN stack (MongoDB, Express, React, Node.js) for the Web Client and Backend Server, alongside React Native for the cross-platform Mobile Application, storing all crucial operational data securely.</p>
